OL,3,CNHS founder's life re-told in theatre
OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,FStarring Michael Sheen, the production
OL,7,Fwill be livestreamed into cinemas next
OL,8,Fmonth under a national theatre scheme
OL,9,Fchampioned by none other than Dame
OL,10,FHelen Mirren
OL,12,FMichael Sheen is portraying Aneurin
OL,13,F'Nye' Bevan - the man who spearheaded
OL,14,Fthe creation of the National Health
OL,15,FService (NHS) - in the National
OL,16,FTheatre's latest play, aptly named Nye.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/9
