OL,3,CNHS founder's life re-told in theatre
OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,FWritten by Tim Price, the production,
OL,7,Faccording to the National Theatre,
OL,8,Ftakes the audience on a "surreal and
OL,9,Fspectacular journey through the life
OL,10,Fand legacy of the man who transformed
OL,11,FBritain's welfare state".
OL,13,FBut, as the Welshman tells ITV News,
OL,14,Fthe timeliness of the show's release
OL,15,Fhas taken on extra importance given
OL,16,Fthe modern-day pressures felt by the
OL,17,FNHS and, what he feels, is the need
OL,18,Ffor radical change.
OL,20,FSheen said: "I think the NHS has to be
OL,21,Freimagined I suppose in many ways.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
