OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F310A1710878565
OL,3,CNHS founder's life re-told in theatre
OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,F"The kind of audacity of Bevan's
OL,7,Fvision and the drive and the
OL,8,Fdetermination to bring those
OL,9,Ffundamental beliefs about: you
OL,10,Fshouldn't be denied basic healthcare
OL,11,Fbecause of your lack of means."
OL,13,FHe added: "We really don't want it to
OL,14,Fgo back to the way it was.
OL,16,F"We talk about people having surgery
OL,17,Fwithout anaesthetic because they
OL,18,Fcouldn't afford it, I mean just awful,
OL,19,Fawful stories and we cannot let things
OL,20,Fgo back to that."
