OL,6,FAudiences can enjoy performances of
OL,7,Fthe play at the National Theatre, in
OL,8,FLondon, up until Saturday May 11,
OL,9,Fbefore it moves to the Wales
OL,10,FMillennium Centre, in Cardiff, for
OL,11,Fseveral weeks.
OL,13,F'The vision that grew out of that has
OL,14,Fto be reimagined now because the NHS
OL,15,Fis in all kinds of difficulties'
OL,17,FAnd, in a quirk organisers hope will
OL,18,Fentice greater viewing interest, the
OL,19,Fproduction is also available to watch
OL,20,Fin selected cinemas.
