OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,FDame Helen Mirren starred in the 2009
OL,7,Fproduction of Phedre, which was then
OL,8,Fthe first play to be broadcast in
OL,9,Fcinemas across the UK.
OL,11,FShe explained to ITV News the
OL,12,Fimportance of bringing such shows to
OL,13,Fthe big screen, enabling future
OL,14,Fgenerations to watch what she hailed
OL,15,Fas "incredible performances".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
