OL,3,CNHS founder's life re-told in theatre
OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,F"Having spent a lot of my career in
OL,7,Ftheatre, having seen incredible
OL,8,Fperformances you know witnessed them
OL,9,Fon stage, acted with the person or
OL,10,Fsitting in the audience and thinking
OL,11,Ffuture generations will never know how
OL,12,Fbrilliant this performance was, was
OL,13,Falways very heartbreaking for me.
OL,15,F"Of course, theatre and film are two
OL,16,Fcompletely different disciplines and
OL,17,Fit's a strange marrying of the two,
OL,18,Fbut at least to save great
OL,19,Fperformances, great plays, great
OL,20,Fproductions for future generations is
OL,21,Fone very important element."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
