OL,6,F'I meet people outside of the stage
OL,7,Fdoor you know saying 'I've been
OL,8,Fworking in the NHS for thirty years or
OL,9,Fmore' and they're so moved by the
OL,10,Fproduction'
OL,12,FAsked about the play's importance in
OL,13,Fhighlighting work done by the NHS,
OL,14,FSheen recounted how an early
OL,15,Fperformance demonstrated a real-life
OL,16,Fexample of the healthcare provided by
OL,17,Fstaff.
