OL,6,FHe said: "Funnily enough on one of the
OL,7,Fearlier performances someone,
OL,8,Funfortunately, got taken quite ill in
OL,9,Fthe theatre and it was towards the end
OL,10,Fof the play and we had to bring the
OL,11,Flights up and everything and stop the
OL,12,Fplay.
OL,14,F"And someone said 'Is there a doctor
OL,15,Fin the house?' and there was about
OL,16,Ffifty of them!
