OL,3,CNHS founder's life re-told in theatre
OL,4,Cproduction starring Michael Sheen
OL,6,F"So, yes, it's well attended anyway.
OL,7,FAnd I meet people outside of the stage
OL,8,Fdoor you know saying 'I've been
OL,9,Fworking in the NHS for thirty years or
OL,10,Fmore' and they're so moved by the
OL,11,Fproduction and they just want to say
OL,12,F'thank you for doing it'.
OL,14,F"But I mean it's just an opportunity
OL,15,Fto say 'thank you' to them for their
OL,16,Fservice."
